CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 2, 1961, pg. 20 reads: "The Picnic Committee - Courier officials and distributors handled the big prize give-away."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the picnic committee including woman and ten men, most holding fishing rods, standing behind prize display of sporting equipment and board games, in South Park for the annual Pittsburgh Courier Newsboys' Picnic
